org.cytoscape.dyn.internal.view.task.interpolator
Class AbstractInterpolator

java.lang.Object
  org.cytoscape.dyn.internal.view.task.interpolator.AbstractInterpolator
Direct Known Subclasses:
BooleanInterpolator, Coordinate2DInterpolator, CoordinateInterpolator, IntegerInterpolator, NormalInterpolator, ScalarInterpolator
public abstract class AbstractInterpolator
extends java.lang.Object

An interpolator that works with positional coordinates.

The interpolation routine is just a simple linear interpolation between each of the points. The interpolator may take arbitrarily spaced keyframes and compute correct values.
